query:
SELECT 
            COUNT(CASE WHEN calories_burned > 400 THEN 1 END) as high_intensity,
            COUNT(CASE WHEN calories_burned BETWEEN 200 AND 400 THEN 1 END) as moderate_intensity
        FROM workout_data 
        WHERE user_id = $1 
        AND created_at >= $2
        AND calories_burned > 200
